data.description:
Welcome to this stunning home with mature landscaping and a meticulously maintained backyard, complete with privacy fencing. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a dramatic two-story entry, setting the stage for falling in love with this popular floor plan.
This home boasts updates throughout, including oak flooring, neutral paint tones, and striking wrought iron stairway spindles. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, ample 42-inch cabinets, granite countertops, and a pantry for added convenience. Natural light floods the great room, accentuating the spaciousness and warmth of this space. Take your pick between formal dining or the ample eat in kitchen space before you step outside to the composite deck or firepit area and take in the breathtaking views. Perfect for entertaining or unwinding after a long day. And for ultimate relaxation, indulge in the luxury of your own hot tub sitting on a 15 x 12 concrete patio. Back inside retreat to the expansive primary suite, offering a five-piece en suite bath and walk in closet. Two more bedrooms and full bath complete the upper level. Additional living space awaits in the finished basement, complete with a family room, full bath, and fourth bedroom, offering versatility and comfort for guests or extended family. For those dry winter months, a built-in humidifier is included and ceiling fans in all rooms ensure comfort in all seasons. This home also boasts a brand- new roof for peace of mind and is conveniently located near popular amenities and major roadways, ensuring easy access to everything you need. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your new home sweet home. Schedule your showing today!
